short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Open images in Google Docs in a new tab

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
As an editor, quickly open embedded images in Google Docs in a new browser tab.
Access the full resolution of images for better clarity and detail.

This plugin is open source
https://github.com/andrewvmail

Bugs and suggestions
